Package: riversCentralAsia
Type: Package
Title: Load, process and visualize data from Central Asian Hydromets
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Tobias Siegfried
Maintainer: Tobias Siegfried <siegfried@hydrosolutions.ch>
Description: Package with helper functions to load, manage and analyze hydrometeorological data from Central Asia. Currently, a relatively complete dataset of the Chirchik River Basin with decadal and monthly data on discharge, precipitation and temperature is included.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  zoo,
  timetk,
  tidyverse,
  lubridate
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
